1
00:00:04,570 --> 00:00:06,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Nice shot, Jakah!</font>

2
00:00:06,090 --> 00:00:06,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yeah!</font>

3
00:00:06,920 --> 00:00:08,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Okay, I'm next!</font>

4
00:00:09,640 --> 00:00:10,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sooha!</font>

5
00:00:10,950 --> 00:00:13,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Shion! Guys!</font>

6
00:00:13,720 --> 00:00:15,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You came to watch us practice?</font>

7
00:00:15,770 --> 00:00:17,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yeah. The game's tomorrow, right?</font>

8
00:00:17,990 --> 00:00:19,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">How are you feeling?</font>

9
00:00:19,450 --> 00:00:20,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Great!</font>

10
00:00:20,600 --> 00:00:23,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You've been missing all your shots.</font>

11
00:00:23,640 --> 00:00:24,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh?</font>

12
00:00:24,420 --> 00:00:25,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Have I?</font>

13
00:00:25,750 --> 00:00:27,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We'll be fine, though.</font>

14
00:00:27,350 --> 00:00:30,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We'll win again, thanks to me.</font>

15
00:00:30,170 --> 00:00:32,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'll dedicate our victory to you.</font>

16
00:00:32,310 --> 00:00:35,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh? R-Really? Thanks.</font>

17
00:00:35,680 --> 00:00:38,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sooha, thanks for coming.</font>

18
00:00:38,510 --> 00:00:40,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">S-Sure.</font>

19
00:00:41,220 --> 00:00:47,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I was born to protect you, 
and I have to keep protecting you.</font>

20
00:00:49,000 --> 00:00:51,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'll do my best, so I hope
 you'll cheer for me.</font>

21
00:00:51,650 --> 00:00:55,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">O-Okay. I really hope you win.</font>

22
00:00:55,220 --> 00:00:56,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yeah.</font>

23
00:00:56,200 --> 00:00:57,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hey.</font>

24
00:00:57,820 --> 00:00:59,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's dangerous for you to be here.</font>

25
00:00:59,580 --> 00:01:01,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If you don't wanna get hurt, stay out.</font>

26
00:01:02,650 --> 00:01:05,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Solon, are you worrying about me?</font>

27
00:01:05,670 --> 00:01:08,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What? No!</font>

28
00:01:08,260 --> 00:01:10,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}Come on, let's practice!</font>

29
00:01:10,490 --> 00:01:11,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}Sure.</font>

30
00:01:11,280 --> 00:01:13,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}Okay, see you guys later.</font>

31
00:01:15,990 --> 00:01:18,970
<font face="Times New Roman" size="23" color="#f9fcfd"><b><font size="25">- Vampire Lord -</font></b></font>

32
00:01:28,210 --> 00:01:30,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's been 120 years.</font>

33
00:01:30,620 --> 00:01:32,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">How have you been, Director?</font>

34
00:01:33,110 --> 00:01:35,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Just fine, as you can see.</font>

35
00:01:35,940 --> 00:01:38,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We thought you'd given up long ago.</font>

36
00:01:39,160 --> 00:01:41,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We had no idea you were 
still looking for us.</font>

37
00:01:41,960 --> 00:01:44,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I didn't come for you boys.</font>

38
00:01:45,350 --> 00:01:47,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm pleased we ran into 
each other, though.</font>

39
00:01:48,620 --> 00:01:50,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I see you all stayed together.</font>

40
00:01:50,700 --> 00:01:52,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What's going on here?</font>

41
00:01:52,470 --> 00:01:54,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We've finally met again.</font>

42
00:01:54,950 --> 00:01:57,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'll tell you boys, as well.</font>

43
00:01:57,610 --> 00:02:01,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You show up outta nowhere and 
want us to hear you out? Screw that!</font>

44
00:02:01,770 --> 00:02:03,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Don't listen to her!</font>

45
00:02:03,770 --> 00:02:05,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We're not listening.</font>

46
00:02:05,350 --> 00:02:07,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Get out of here.</font>

47
00:02:08,070 --> 00:02:12,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We're not the kids you knew anymore.</font>

48
00:02:17,320 --> 00:02:20,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">There are more pressing matters right now.</font>

49
00:02:33,750 --> 00:02:34,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Khan!</font>

50
00:02:35,050 --> 00:02:36,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sorry for suddenly asking to meet.</font>

51
00:02:36,730 --> 00:02:37,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Did something happen?</font>

52
00:02:38,180 --> 00:02:39,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Well, actually...</font>

53
00:02:40,210 --> 00:02:43,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I just really wanted 
to tell you something.</font>

54
00:02:45,240 --> 00:02:48,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I love you, Sooha.</font>

55
00:02:48,350 --> 00:02:49,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What?</font>

56
00:02:50,660 --> 00:02:55,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Werewolves fall in love for life.</font>

57
00:02:56,530 --> 00:03:00,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So I'll keep loving you until I die.</font>

58
00:03:02,980 --> 00:03:08,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'd be really happy if you cheered for
 me at our upcoming nightball game.</font>

59
00:03:10,490 --> 00:03:13,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's all I wanted to say.</font>

60
00:03:16,940 --> 00:03:19,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'll walk you back.</font>

61
00:03:29,220 --> 00:03:33,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>At last, tonight is the nightball final!</i></font>

62
00:03:33,580 --> 00:03:38,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Once again, Sunshine City School 
faces off against Decelis Academy!</i></font>

63
00:03:40,530 --> 00:03:43,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I'll do my best, so I hope
 you'll cheer for me.</i></font>

64
00:03:43,600 --> 00:03:46,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I'd be really happy if you cheered for me.</i></font>

65
00:03:46,910 --> 00:03:48,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>What should I do?</i></font>

66
00:03:48,440 --> 00:03:51,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I treasure my friendship 
with both of them.</i></font>

67
00:03:51,850 --> 00:03:53,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>At least, that's what I thought.</i></font>

68
00:03:53,920 --> 00:03:56,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>But they're important to me as...</i></font>

69
00:03:58,300 --> 00:04:00,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I should focus on cheering right now!</font>

70
00:04:02,820 --> 00:04:06,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Will last year's champions, 
Decelis, repeat their success?</i></font>

71
00:04:06,740 --> 00:04:09,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Or will Sunshine City get revenge?</i></font>

72
00:04:09,710 --> 00:04:13,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>This red-hot game will 
be kicking off shortly!</i></font>

73
00:04:14,330 --> 00:04:17,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Mahan, Rusland, Kamil...</i></font>

74
00:04:18,730 --> 00:04:21,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>You promised you'd be back.</i></font>

75
00:04:21,430 --> 00:04:23,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>No. I have to focus!</i></font>

76
00:04:23,150 --> 00:04:25,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We're going to win this game!</font>

77
00:04:25,640 --> 00:04:28,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We'll easily beat you again this year!</font>

78
00:04:28,050 --> 00:04:28,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh?</font>

79
00:04:28,870 --> 00:04:33,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sooha! Our team's supporters 
are sitting over there!</font>

80
00:04:34,940 --> 00:04:39,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Sooha, I promise I'll win for you.</i></font>

81
00:04:39,630 --> 00:04:40,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>What should I do?</i></font>

82
00:04:43,130 --> 00:04:46,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>The game is about to begin!</i></font>

83
00:05:01,010 --> 00:05:04,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Whoa! Will Decelis score here?!</i></font>

84
00:05:05,400 --> 00:05:07,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Jino! Over here!</font>

85
00:05:08,460 --> 00:05:08,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Nice!</font>

86
00:05:11,180 --> 00:05:15,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Sunshine hits back! 
What a powerful tackle!</i></font>

87
00:05:11,490 --> 00:05:12,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}Shion!</font>

88
00:05:15,010 --> 00:05:16,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Nice, Khan!</font>

89
00:05:16,120 --> 00:05:17,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Enzy!</font>

90
00:05:22,120 --> 00:05:22,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Damn!</font>

91
00:05:30,610 --> 00:05:32,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Decelis scores first!</i></font>

92
00:05:32,660 --> 00:05:33,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Nice, Heli.</font>

93
00:05:33,440 --> 00:05:33,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Thanks.</font>

94
00:05:33,980 --> 00:05:35,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Not bad!</font>

95
00:05:36,820 --> 00:05:38,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Heli...</font>

96
00:05:53,080 --> 00:05:56,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>The first half ends with 
Decelis leading by one!</i></font>

97
00:05:57,750 --> 00:06:00,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>That was rougher than I expected.</i></font>

98
00:06:00,640 --> 00:06:02,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I hope nobody gets hurt.</i></font>

99
00:06:02,750 --> 00:06:03,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sooha!</font>

100
00:06:03,970 --> 00:06:06,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Did you see me score earlier?</font>

101
00:06:06,590 --> 00:06:08,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yeah! You were awesome!</font>

102
00:06:08,840 --> 00:06:09,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Right?</font>

103
00:06:09,990 --> 00:06:12,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I scored our second point.</font>

104
00:06:12,510 --> 00:06:13,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sooha!</font>

105
00:06:13,830 --> 00:06:16,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Our team's sitting over there!</font>

106
00:06:16,340 --> 00:06:17,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, um...</font>

107
00:06:17,560 --> 00:06:18,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sooha!</font>

108
00:06:18,850 --> 00:06:22,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We're trailing for now, but I swear
 we'll win, so cheer for me!</font>

109
00:06:22,940 --> 00:06:26,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What? Sooha's rooting for us.</font>

110
00:06:26,660 --> 00:06:29,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sooha, our team's sitting on that side!</font>

111
00:06:29,310 --> 00:06:29,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hey!</font>

112
00:06:29,920 --> 00:06:31,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sooha's with us.</font>

113
00:06:32,190 --> 00:06:34,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sooha, are you having fun?</font>

114
00:06:34,120 --> 00:06:35,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Heli?!</font>

115
00:06:38,100 --> 00:06:39,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Cheer for us, okay?</font>

116
00:06:40,930 --> 00:06:41,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">See you later.</font>

117
00:06:41,700 --> 00:06:43,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's all?</font>

118
00:06:46,890 --> 00:06:47,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Heli...</font>

119
00:06:49,670 --> 00:06:50,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sooha.</font>

120
00:06:52,670 --> 00:06:53,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Do you have a moment?</font>

121
00:06:54,950 --> 00:06:58,910
<font face="Times New Roman" size="13"><b>{\an8}- Dark Moon: The Blood Altar -</b></font>

122
00:06:58,950 --> 00:07:02,900
<font face="Times New Roman" size="13"><b>{\an8}- Dark Moon: The Blood Altar -</b></font>

123
00:07:06,360 --> 00:07:07,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No...</font>

124
00:07:08,470 --> 00:07:11,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's why I've been looking for you.</font>

125
00:07:20,540 --> 00:07:21,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No!</font>

126
00:07:24,420 --> 00:07:27,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>What? That was Sooha.</i></font>

127
00:07:28,420 --> 00:07:29,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>She's not there.</i></font>

128
00:07:33,170 --> 00:07:35,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>She's gone. She's gone.</i></font>

129
00:07:35,950 --> 00:07:36,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Sooha!</i></font>

130
00:07:44,820 --> 00:07:46,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Heli!</font>

131
00:07:46,600 --> 00:07:48,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Are you okay?!</font>

132
00:07:48,790 --> 00:07:50,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">S-Sooha is...</font>

133
00:07:50,750 --> 00:07:53,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I won't let them take it today!</i></font>

134
00:07:54,170 --> 00:07:56,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I have to win!</i></font>

135
00:07:57,940 --> 00:08:00,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Goal!</i></font>

136
00:08:00,160 --> 00:08:02,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Sunshine City scores the goal 
they desperately wanted!</i></font>

137
00:08:00,490 --> 00:08:01,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}Yes!</font>

138
00:08:02,110 --> 00:08:04,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}That was amazing, Khan!</font>

139
00:08:02,730 --> 00:08:07,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Sunshine City gets revenge!</i></font>

140
00:08:04,290 --> 00:08:05,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}Damn.</font>

141
00:08:06,140 --> 00:08:07,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}We almost had them.</font>

142
00:08:07,290 --> 00:08:17,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}Sunshine! Sunshine! Sunshine!</font>

143
00:08:11,650 --> 00:08:13,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Heli, is something wrong?</font>

144
00:08:13,970 --> 00:08:16,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Something happened.</font>

145
00:08:17,900 --> 00:08:21,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sooha!</font>

146
00:08:27,730 --> 00:08:29,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Why were you with Sooha?</font>

147
00:08:29,990 --> 00:08:31,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Who took her?</font>

148
00:08:33,460 --> 00:08:36,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Dardan, the First Vampire.</font>

149
00:08:37,220 --> 00:08:40,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Dardan, the First Vampire? Who's that?</font>

150
00:08:40,740 --> 00:08:41,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Could it be...</font>

151
00:08:41,950 --> 00:08:46,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You really don't know anything, do you?</font>

152
00:08:49,190 --> 00:08:52,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Dardan was a chancellor of 
the ancient Vargr Kingdom.</font>

153
00:08:53,630 --> 00:08:57,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Though he was originally human, 
in pursuit of power,</font>

154
00:08:57,650 --> 00:09:01,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">he turned himself into a vampire 
using a forbidden method.</font>

155
00:09:03,240 --> 00:09:04,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That must be him.</font>

156
00:09:04,690 --> 00:09:05,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You've met him?</font>

157
00:09:05,850 --> 00:09:10,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yeah. He attacked us with 
a horde of vampires.</font>

158
00:09:10,870 --> 00:09:12,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Who were those vampires with him?</font>

159
00:09:13,210 --> 00:09:18,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Lesser vampires created by Dardan.</font>

160
00:09:18,930 --> 00:09:22,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Weak to sunlight and 
with no sense of reason,</font>

161
00:09:22,760 --> 00:09:25,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">they can't suppress 
their thirst for blood.</font>

162
00:09:26,920 --> 00:09:28,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You understand, don't you?</font>

163
00:09:28,290 --> 00:09:32,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That you're different from those vampires.</font>

164
00:09:33,160 --> 00:09:37,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You are vampire lords of 
the ancient Vargr Kingdom.</font>

165
00:09:38,070 --> 00:09:40,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Vampire lords?</font>

166
00:09:40,720 --> 00:09:46,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes. You were also knights 
who served the princess.</font>

167
00:09:46,390 --> 00:09:49,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You imprisoned us! 
We don't believe anything—</font>

168
00:09:49,140 --> 00:09:51,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}I wasn't imprisoning you.</font>

169
00:09:51,640 --> 00:09:55,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I kept you at Vanfield to 
protect you from Dardan.</font>

170
00:09:56,660 --> 00:10:01,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Over a millennium ago, when Dardan's 
rebellion threatened the kingdom,</font>

171
00:10:01,670 --> 00:10:06,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">the princess sent your souls into 
the distant future to protect you.</font>

172
00:10:07,450 --> 00:10:13,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">However, you lost your memories 
and reverted to infancy.</font>

173
00:10:14,210 --> 00:10:21,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I tracked down every last one of you 
and protected you at Vanfield House.</font>

174
00:10:22,580 --> 00:10:26,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Princess? Wait a minute.</font>

175
00:10:26,310 --> 00:10:28,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That princess...</font>

176
00:10:28,020 --> 00:10:29,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Is she...</font>

177
00:10:30,970 --> 00:10:33,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Is she Sooha?</font>

178
00:10:33,770 --> 00:10:39,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes. I tracked the princess's energy here.</font>

179
00:10:39,930 --> 00:10:43,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You must've known 
instinctively, as well...</font>

180
00:10:43,400 --> 00:10:46,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">what your destinies are.</font>

181
00:10:55,060 --> 00:10:58,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So, why did Dardan kidnap Sooha?</font>

182
00:10:59,310 --> 00:11:01,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The same reason he did in the past.</font>

183
00:11:01,510 --> 00:11:05,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Dardan is trying to acquire her power.</font>

184
00:11:05,140 --> 00:11:08,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Now everything will be mine.</i></font>

185
00:11:09,070 --> 00:11:11,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The princess... Dardan...</font>

186
00:11:11,510 --> 00:11:12,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I see.</font>

187
00:11:41,990 --> 00:11:44,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">There you are, Your Highness.</font>

188
00:11:45,880 --> 00:11:46,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sir Heli.</font>

189
00:11:47,490 --> 00:11:49,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The queen is calling for you.</font>

190
00:11:49,830 --> 00:11:51,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It must be about... that.</font>

191
00:11:53,110 --> 00:11:57,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The prince of a neighboring 
kingdom proposed.</font>

192
00:11:57,690 --> 00:12:02,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes, I've heard. 
They say he's a great man.</font>

193
00:12:02,670 --> 00:12:05,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But I don't want to get married yet.</font>

194
00:12:06,680 --> 00:12:11,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And I can't promise my life 
to someone I hardly know.</font>

195
00:12:11,830 --> 00:12:15,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But I'm not allowed to choose who I love.</font>

196
00:12:16,870 --> 00:12:22,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm sure you'll meet someone you can 
love from the bottom of your heart.</font>

197
00:12:22,950 --> 00:12:27,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Perhaps I should tell Mother how I...</font>

198
00:12:27,680 --> 00:12:28,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Your Highness!</font>

199
00:12:31,150 --> 00:12:32,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What's wrong?</font>

200
00:12:33,230 --> 00:12:35,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Thank you, Sir Heli.</font>

201
00:12:36,380 --> 00:12:40,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're always rescuing me.</font>

202
00:12:43,310 --> 00:12:46,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's my job to protect you, Your Highness.</font>

203
00:12:59,570 --> 00:13:03,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You look lovely as always 
today, Princess Selen.</font>

204
00:13:03,800 --> 00:13:06,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Will you be accepting 
the prince's proposal?</font>

205
00:13:06,760 --> 00:13:11,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Chancellor Dardan, 
I respectfully declined his offer.</font>

206
00:13:11,210 --> 00:13:13,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's good news.</font>

207
00:13:14,510 --> 00:13:17,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I didn't think you'd do as I wanted.</font>

208
00:13:17,660 --> 00:13:19,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's none of your business!</font>

209
00:13:19,530 --> 00:13:22,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I agree with you, Princess Selen.</font>

210
00:13:22,730 --> 00:13:25,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm opposed to political marriages.</font>

211
00:13:26,700 --> 00:13:28,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You eavesdropped on me?!</font>

212
00:13:28,450 --> 00:13:32,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I just naturally hear your voice.</font>

213
00:13:32,450 --> 00:13:33,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Why?</font>

214
00:13:34,270 --> 00:13:36,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Because I'm always listening for it.</font>

215
00:13:36,000 --> 00:13:37,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">How rude!</font>

216
00:13:38,670 --> 00:13:40,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Rude?</font>

217
00:13:41,150 --> 00:13:43,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Because I'm not royalty?</font>

218
00:13:44,530 --> 00:13:47,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So status <i>is</i> important to you!</font>

219
00:13:47,090 --> 00:13:48,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Unhand me!</font>

220
00:13:49,930 --> 00:13:53,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">How can I make your heart mine—</font>

221
00:13:54,460 --> 00:13:55,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Dardan!</font>

222
00:13:55,720 --> 00:14:00,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The next time you disrespect the 
princess like that, you'll pay dearly!</font>

223
00:14:06,290 --> 00:14:08,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He's unbelievable.</font>

224
00:14:10,900 --> 00:14:11,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Your Highness!</font>

225
00:14:14,930 --> 00:14:18,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Selen! Selen, please hold on!</font>

226
00:14:20,770 --> 00:14:22,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It is as we feared.</font>

227
00:14:22,850 --> 00:14:23,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What is this?</font>

228
00:14:23,980 --> 00:14:27,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I believe it's due to the royal 
bloodline's shamanistic powers.</font>

229
00:14:28,980 --> 00:14:33,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Princess Selen's powers are the 
strongest the kingdom has ever seen.</font>

230
00:14:33,400 --> 00:14:36,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Her body can no longer withstand them.</font>

231
00:14:37,530 --> 00:14:39,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">At this rate, she'll die.</font>

232
00:14:40,730 --> 00:14:43,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">There's only one way to keep her alive.</font>

233
00:14:44,110 --> 00:14:47,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We'll use the blood of the kingdom's 
treasured ancient wolf god...</font>

234
00:14:48,550 --> 00:14:50,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The blood of Vargr.</font>

235
00:14:59,450 --> 00:15:00,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Selen!</font>

236
00:15:02,990 --> 00:15:06,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>What is this? I feel so warm...</i></font>

237
00:15:06,620 --> 00:15:11,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Your Highness, you are Selen, 
the princess who carries shaman's blood.</font>

238
00:15:12,590 --> 00:15:16,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I, Vargr the wolf god, 
shall grant you strength.</font>

239
00:15:17,480 --> 00:15:19,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're Vargr?</font>

240
00:15:26,480 --> 00:15:29,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Selen, you're awake!</font>

241
00:15:30,070 --> 00:15:32,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Thank goodness. You're all right now.</font>

242
00:15:32,670 --> 00:15:37,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Mother, I met the god Vargr.</font>

243
00:15:38,060 --> 00:15:41,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">O great Vargr, thank you.</font>

244
00:15:45,190 --> 00:15:49,170
<font size="20"><b>{\an8}<font size="21"><font face="Times New Roman">One Year Later</font></font></b></font>

245
00:15:50,120 --> 00:15:52,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Mother! Mother!</font>

246
00:15:53,590 --> 00:15:57,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Selen, don't be so sad.</font>

247
00:15:58,060 --> 00:16:03,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You know this is the only way.</font>

248
00:16:03,060 --> 00:16:04,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Mother...</font>

249
00:16:05,150 --> 00:16:10,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Now that he's become First Vampire, 
Dardan is trying to take over the kingdom.</font>

250
00:16:11,380 --> 00:16:17,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The werewolves aided us, 
but their numbers were too great.</font>

251
00:16:18,790 --> 00:16:24,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So you gave them your blood...</font>

252
00:16:34,760 --> 00:16:38,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">and created new vampire lords.</font>

253
00:16:39,830 --> 00:16:43,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Please, work together...</font>

254
00:16:45,060 --> 00:16:49,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">to protect this nation from Dardan.</font>

255
00:16:53,400 --> 00:16:55,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But I'm just...</font>

256
00:16:55,710 --> 00:16:58,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">By drinking Vargr's blood,</font>

257
00:16:59,400 --> 00:17:05,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">you acquired the power of the ancient 
wolf god and became a vampire queen.</font>

258
00:17:05,950 --> 00:17:11,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Selen, take my shamanistic power.</font>

259
00:17:12,190 --> 00:17:17,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">My power has already been 
sealed in the moon altar.</font>

260
00:17:17,920 --> 00:17:19,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Mother...</font>

261
00:17:19,450 --> 00:17:26,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Selen, if I die, you must hold a 
coronation ceremony at the moon altar,</font>

262
00:17:26,690 --> 00:17:30,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">break the seal,
 receive the queen's power,</font>

263
00:17:31,310 --> 00:17:34,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">and become the most 
powerful queen of all time.</font>

264
00:17:36,260 --> 00:17:38,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Don't worry, Your Majesty.</font>

265
00:17:39,010 --> 00:17:44,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I shall claim that power 
and rule this kingdom well.</font>

266
00:17:44,930 --> 00:17:45,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Dardan!</font>

267
00:17:45,710 --> 00:17:50,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Princess Selen, I didn't want to do this.</font>

268
00:17:50,620 --> 00:17:55,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I simply wanted your love, but you 
wouldn't so much as glance my way.</font>

269
00:17:55,870 --> 00:17:56,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Step back!</font>

270
00:18:00,220 --> 00:18:01,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Marge!</font>

271
00:18:02,470 --> 00:18:07,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So the only way to make you mine 
is to take you and crush you.</font>

272
00:18:13,700 --> 00:18:15,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Protect the princess!</font>

273
00:18:25,160 --> 00:18:26,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Heli, get the princess!</font>

274
00:18:27,060 --> 00:18:28,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Your Highness, are you all right?</font>

275
00:18:28,960 --> 00:18:30,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Dardan, you bastard!</font>

276
00:18:30,830 --> 00:18:32,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Stay out of my way!</font>

277
00:18:35,000 --> 00:18:36,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sir Heli!</font>

278
00:18:36,460 --> 00:18:41,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You also love the princess, 
so you must understand.</font>

279
00:18:41,090 --> 00:18:45,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You alone should admit I'm right.</font>

280
00:18:48,970 --> 00:18:50,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Bastard...</font>

281
00:18:58,950 --> 00:19:02,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Now everything will be mine.</font>

282
00:19:02,870 --> 00:19:05,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Princess! To the moon altar!</font>

283
00:19:05,120 --> 00:19:06,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You must hurry!</font>

284
00:19:07,670 --> 00:19:09,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Your Highness! Your Highness!</font>

285
00:19:24,630 --> 00:19:26,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Marge, your back!</font>

286
00:19:26,110 --> 00:19:29,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hurry... The coronation...</font>

287
00:19:29,750 --> 00:19:31,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I can't!</font>

288
00:19:31,190 --> 00:19:35,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I can't sacrifice everyone 
to become queen!</font>

289
00:19:38,650 --> 00:19:41,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Marge, I have a request.</font>

290
00:19:42,140 --> 00:19:44,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm going to return to the palace</font>

291
00:19:44,520 --> 00:19:47,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">and send the knights' souls 
into the distant future.</font>

292
00:19:48,410 --> 00:19:54,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">When the time comes, 
please find them and protect them.</font>

293
00:19:54,810 --> 00:19:55,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Your Highness...</font>

294
00:20:04,650 --> 00:20:06,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You'll pay for this!</font>

295
00:20:06,180 --> 00:20:10,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">For you, there's no limit 
to how cruel I can be.</font>

296
00:20:14,230 --> 00:20:16,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Stay down!</font>

297
00:20:24,510 --> 00:20:25,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Your Highness!</font>

298
00:20:28,730 --> 00:20:37,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sir Heli, you've saved me 
from danger so many times...</font>

299
00:20:38,380 --> 00:20:41,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">without any fear or hesitation.</font>

300
00:20:42,390 --> 00:20:48,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I know you've been hiding something...</font>

301
00:20:49,340 --> 00:20:54,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">because I've been hiding the same thing.</font>

302
00:20:55,670 --> 00:20:58,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Next time, please...</font>

303
00:20:58,880 --> 00:21:02,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Let us be our true selves.</font>

304
00:21:25,370 --> 00:21:31,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Dardan tried to take Sooha's shamanistic 
powers and the power of Vargr.</font>

305
00:21:32,290 --> 00:21:33,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes.</font>

306
00:21:35,100 --> 00:21:38,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I see. That legend...</font>

307
00:21:38,660 --> 00:21:40,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It was about us.</font>

308
00:23:34,030 --> 00:23:39,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Next time, Episode 9: 
"Misty Moon: The Black Mist of Railgun."</i></font>

309
00:23:36,950 --> 00:23:40,250
